hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: In a meeting expressdoctor.co.uk That Headless Horseman is coming back for something important (think about it). And he’s extremely dangerous. This is where Kurtzman and Orci put in more complex mythology and, once you’ve come up with this kind of premise, there has to be more to it, so no fault there. It’s just that all the chills and gore are, at this point, less appealing than the fish out of water story and the human relationship between Crane and Abbie. There so much to mine about waking up and asking a detective if he knows George Washington.
